		{ value: `43%`, label: `come to faith before age 13, yet only about 1 in 4 believers convert after age 21` },
		{ value: `1:5`, label: `the average is one volunteer for every five children each week — a ratio few ministries can sustain` },
		{ value: `43%`, label: `of churchgoers say children’s programs are a “very important” reason they attend — a weight you feel` },
